<p><a href="#sdfootnote30anc" name="sdfootnote30sym">30</a> David Green i Joanna Lowry, <em>From Presence to the Performative. Rethinking Photographic Indexicality</em>, w: <em>Where is the Photograph?</em>, Photoforum Maidstone/Photoworks, Brighton-Maidstone 2003, s. 48.</p>
